===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Volkner (Masters)}}
Volkner forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Luxray}}, {{p|Electivire}}, and {{p|Raichu}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Volkner became a playable sync pair on September 30, 2020.

Volkner has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

